thread.title: John Rafferty

author: John Rafferty
title: John Rafferty
text: The services at Servcorp Bondi and the delivery of those by the staff at Bondi Junction are excellent. Having services that are high quality, flexible and practical is particularly important if you are not in the one location and need to travel out of Sydney to see clients. You can depend that the clients will be well catered for during your absence and enjoy all of the benefits that come with a modern city office facility. Highly recommended.
